{"bangumi":{"date":"2012-12-25","platform":"WEB","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/20/ba/59160_cEF9y.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/20/ba/59160_cEF9y.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/20/ba/59160_cEF9y.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/20/ba/59160_cEF9y.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/20/ba/59160_cEF9y.jpg"},"summary":"　　據海外媒體報道，國際著名視頻網站YouTube的日本公司於今年12月開通了一個全新的動畫頻道“動畫番長（Anime Bancho）”。12月25日，負責運營“動畫番長”的日本影視發行公司CoMix Wave Films宣布，他們將在該頻道中推出一部系列原創動畫短片《地獄警察（Inferno Cop）》。\r\n　　《地獄警察》是一個每集長3分鐘的動畫短片系列，由CoMix Wave Films和動畫公司Trigger合作推出，預定於每周二在“動畫番長”頻道中播出一集。“動畫番長”雖然是在日本開設的動畫頻道，但運營宗旨是面向全球用戶，因此頻道中播出的動畫都配有英文字幕，本次的新片也不例外。\r\n　　動畫《地獄警察》以正義腐朽、邪惡橫行的城市“彈簧刀鋒鎮（Jackknife Edge Town）”作為舞台，主人公“地獄警察”要以自己的方式改變這條黑暗的街道。《地獄警察》由日本新銳動畫公司Trigger負責制作，總制作人由《劇場版天元突破》導演今石洋之擔任。","name":"インフェルノコップ","name_cn":"地狱刑事","tags":[{"name":"TRIGGER","count":116,"total_cont":0},{"name":"今石洋之","count":90,"total_cont":0},{"name":"泡面番","count":88,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":73,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2012","count":64,"total_cont":0},{"name":"WEB","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":43,"total_cont":0},{"name":"雨宮哲","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"雨宫哲","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2012年12月","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"静止","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2013年1月","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2012年","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"纸片","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"季番","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"警察","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"泡面","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动作","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"若林広海","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2012年10月","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短片","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0}